ve_coding"},{"short_id":"mwntzg","created_at":"2026-03-15T12:27:56.000-05:00","title":"ksynth","url":"https://octetta.github.io/k-synth/","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"\u003cp\u003eQuick path to an audio payoff:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClick \"patches\" and choose dm-bell.ks.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClick \"run\"—the notebook area will update. Click the waveform to hear the result.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClick the \"-\u0026gt;0\" button below the waveform to copy it into slot 0 at the top (slots are also clickable).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClick \"pads\" in the entry area to show a performance grid.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClick \"melodic\" to play slot 0's sample at different intervals across the grid.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","description_plain":"Quick path to an audio payoff:\r\n\r\n- Click \"patches\" and choose dm-bell.ks.\r\n- Click \"run\"—the notebook area will update. Click the waveform to hear the result.\r\n- Click the \"-\u003e0\" button below the waveform to copy it into slot 0 at the top (slots are also clickable).\r\n- Click \"pads\" in the entry area to show a performance grid.\r\n- Click \"melodic\" to play slot 0's sample at different intervals across the grid.","submitter_user":"veqq","user_is_author":false,"tags":["apl","vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/mwntzg","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/mwntzg/ksynth"},{"short_id":"oahtd6","created_at":"2026-03-15T12:16:39.000-05:00","title":"Codegen is not productivity","url":"https://www.antifound.com/posts/codegen-is-not-productivity/","score":13,"flags":0,"comment_count":1,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"rau","user_is_author":false,"tags":["vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/oahtd6","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/oahtd6/codegen_is_not_productivity"},{"short_id":"pk2axu","created_at":"2026-03-15T08:59:00.000-05:00","title":"Separating the Wayland Compositor and W